Installation:

	git clone git://github.com/moshpitsurfer/dotvim.git ~/.vim

Create symlinks:

	ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc

Switch to the `~/.vim` directory, and fetch submodules:

	cd ~/.vim
	git submodule init
	git submodule update

Load documentation:

	Open vim and type :Helptags

Some suggestions:

	Add new snippets at snippets folder

	Add file-type specific plugins at ftplugins

	Install powerline fonts
		apt-get install fonts-powerline (debian)
